{
  "abstract": "A rapid procedure is proposed for simultaneous determination of NH4-,\r\nNO~-, and NO3-N in field moist samples. The procedure involves extraction,\r\nwith Morgan's solution followed by determination of NH4-N by Nessler's\r\nreagent, NO2-N by x-naphthylamine and sulphanilic acid and NOa-N by\r\nphenol-disulphoric acid. The method will suit small laboratories and 50 to 75\r\nsamples can be analysed in a day.",
